messages.messageBody:
I posted some pictures of our last unschooling group potluck. I think
the album is called "North Idaho Unschoolers". We tye-died T-shirts but
our kids all went crazy and decided to tye-dye themselves! I am so so
lucky to have a group of friends up here who all unschool and are ok
with having their kids dyed bright red and green.

-Alice
North Idaho Unschoolers
http://groups.yahoo.com/group/NorthIdahoUnschoolers/

pictures.
